Question: Develop an argument for or against the following statement: television violence is appropriate for audiences of all ages
Answer:
Television violence may be effective in relieving stress but it is not appropriate  for aduiances of all ages.  First of all, as Psychology study shows that children who observed violent behavior actually became more aggressive in game. Long term explosure of TV violence  are likely to have detrimental effects on children. Seniors on the other hand may not be able to resist the violence.